{"tid":1223572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家真係要好好珍惜現家","createTime":"2019-06-14T17:38:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T20:54:55.000Z","uid":247521,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"228b7a3612db0bb70f451dc54537f5232eedb562","tid":1223572,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T17:38:54.000Z","msg":"我唔敢講會輸 <br />\n<br />\n但係大家諗下 如果今次輸左<br />\n<br />\n香港就好似大陸咁 <br />\n<br />\nGoogle YouTube 可以接觸外國消息既渠道都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人就會變到好似大陸人一樣 乜柒都唔知  連64都唔會知<br />\n<br />\n睇新聞永遠都係講中國幾強大 講外國幾撚衰 幾撚賤 <br />\n<br />\n每個人連立場都冇埋。講每一句野都要慎言 <br />\n<br />\n所以我真係想呼籲大家<br />\n<br />\n6.16 一定要出黎 <br />\n因為今次遊行係合法 <br />\n無危險性 (可以叫埋上次因爲怕危險既朋友）<br />\n<br />\n加油啦 香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8037dcacb71baaaf20da1708498ce445c9565a10","tid":1223572,"uid":312253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:46:07.000Z","msg":"之前既你去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045b8126e212f2e88fa77d90610609d6ef1af6a4","tid":1223572,"uid":247521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8037dcacb71baaaf20da1708498ce445c9565a10","tid":1223572,"uid":312253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T09:46:07.000Z","msg":"之前既你去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T20:54:55.000Z","msg":"可唔可番黎我身邊？"}]}